'From Squeak3.3alpha of 11 January 2002 [latest update: #4873] on 17 May 2002 at 11:52:19 am'!"Change Set:		addEToyFlaps-mirDate:			17 May 2002Author:			Michael RuegerRefixing a problem with automatically adding etoy flaps."!!Flaps class methodsFor: 'predefined flaps' stamp: 'mir 5/14/2002 14:37'!addAndEnableEToyFlaps	"Initialize the standard default out-of-box set of global flaps.  This method creates them and places them in my class variable #SharedFlapTabs, but does not itself get them displayed."	SharedFlapTabs		ifNotNil: [^self].	SharedFlapTabs _ OrderedCollection new.	SharedFlapTabs add: self newSuppliesFlap.	SharedFlapTabs add: self newWidgetsFlap.	SharedFlapTabs add: self newNavigatorFlap.	self enableGlobalFlapWithID: 'Supplies'.	self enableGlobalFlapWithID: 'Navigator'.	self enableGlobalFlapWithID: 'Widgets'.	SharedFlapsAllowed _ true.	Project current flapsSuppressed: false.	^ SharedFlapTabs"Flaps addAndEnableEToyFlaps"! !